[Kamiya Satoshi](http://www.folders.jp/)'s [Pegasus](http://www.folders.jp/g/2002/0241.html), folded from a square from A4 standard paper (21x21 cm square). The model is about 8 cm long. Satoshi suggests 25x25 paper, which obviously must be thinner than 80g/m^2. But the model itself is wonderful, although my rendition of may not be worth of it.  
  
